## 5. Frontend Design System

The application uses a **Cyberpunk/Sci-Fi** aesthetic designed for immersive user engagement.

### 5.1 Technology Stack
| Layer | Technology | Purpose |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **Templates** | **Blade** | Laravel's templating engine for server-side rendering |
| **Styling** | **Tailwind CSS 4.0** | Utility-first CSS framework |
| **Interactivity** | **Alpine.js** | Lightweight JavaScript for modals and toggles |
| **Build Tool** | **Vite** | Fast asset bundling with hot module replacement |

